.DT
set_list_function
Disk World creator help
set_list_function

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_list_function -  This method sets the function to call when listing something.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_list_function(mixed func)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^func%^RESET%^ - the function to call
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the function to call when listing something.  The
function will be called with two elements, the first being the
player doing the listing and the second being the array
of objects being listed.


If the function is a string then the function of that name will be called on the shop, if it is a function pointer then the function pointer will be evaluated.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_sell_function(), set_value_function(), set_too_costly_function(), set_cannot_sell_function() , set_browse_function(), set_list_function()

.EP

